articles.description: According to the fact-checking platform BOOM, the original video belonged to a social media influencer, and Kajol's face was digitally inserted into the footage.
articles.content: After Rashmika Mandanna and Katrina Kaif, Kajol has become the latest victim of deepfake videos. The internet has undergone a significant shift in the past month, witnessing a surge in deepfake video… [+755 chars]
